title: Iman Honors David Bowie On The One-Year Anniversary Of His Death | PerezHilton.com
text:
Although no one feels the pain quite like Iman , we can't believe it's already been a year since the world lost David Bowie .
Proving that her legendary husband of 24 years is gone but never forgotten, the 61-year-old shared a stunning photo of a double rainbow over the New York City skyline on the one-year anniversary of the Let's Dance singer's death.
As you may remember, Bowie passed away at the age of 69 on January 10, 2016 after a private battle with liver cancer.
